msgid "Please hurry, or my sister will kill us both."
msgstr "急いで、じゃないと僕らが姉さんに殺される。"

msgid "Here or outside is fine."
msgstr "ここでも外でもいいよ。"

msgid "We really appreciate it."
msgstr "本当にありがとう。"

msgid "Hurry the hell up already!"
msgstr "さっさと行きなさいよ！"

msgid "What are you doing?"
msgstr "何してんの？"

msgid "Don't babysit him, KILL HIM!"
msgstr "世話しろなんて言ってない、殺すのよ！"

msgid "Oh my god. The silence. It's so damn good."
msgstr "あぁすごい。静寂。もう最高。"

msgid "Here you go, you earned it."
msgstr "ほらこれ、お礼。"

msgid "Not sure why you'd want this though."
msgstr "なんで欲しいのかは知らないけど。"

msgid "Thanks."
msgstr "ありがとう。"

msgid "Thank the cursed heavens it's gone."
msgstr "消えてくれて、クソったれの天に感謝ね。"

msgid "Alright, I guess I'll just..."
msgstr "わかった、やるよ……"

msgid "Yes, kill it. Do it."
msgstr "そう、殺して。ほら。"

msgid "Quickly."
msgstr "早く。"

msgid "HUZZAH!!!!!"
msgstr "おっしゃああああ!!!!!"

msgid "Finally."
msgstr "ついに。"

msgid "Dead dead dead!"
msgstr "死んだ死んだ死んだ！"

msgid "You'll kill him???"
msgstr "殺してくれるの???"

msgid "I guess so."
msgstr "まあ、うん。"

msgid "THANK THE HEAVENS."
msgstr "やった、最高。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.event_take_caterpillar.dlg.ch1_terrarium"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "You shut the hell up. You're dead meat, jerk."
msgstr "黙りなさい。あんたはもう死んでんの。"

msgid "Farewell, little brother. It has been a displeasure."
msgstr "さようなら弟、おまえといられて最悪だったよ。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.event_take_caterpillar.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "(What now...?)"
msgstr "(どうしよう……？)"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.event_take_caterpillar.choice.(What now...?)"
msgid "Kill it here"
msgstr "ここで殺す"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.event_take_caterpillar.choice.(What now...?)"
msgid "Do not"
msgstr "やめておく"

msgid "Why're you carrying a bucket?"
msgstr "なんでバケツなんか持ち歩いてんの？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.item_bucket_on_moth_girl.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "(To be honest, I'm not so sure myself.)"
msgstr "(正直、自分でもよくわからない。)"

msgid "(Um...)"
msgstr "(うーん……)"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.item_caterpillar.choice.(Um...)"
msgid "Kill it here"
msgstr "ここで殺す"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.item_caterpillar.choice.(Um...)"
msgid "Do not"
msgstr "やめておく"

msgid "What's taking so long?!"
msgstr "何ぐずぐずしてんのよ!?"

msgid "...Damn. That was pretty metal."
msgstr "……やるわね。最高にロックじゃない。"

msgid "It stinks though."
msgstr "ひどい臭いだけど。"

msgid "No take backs!"
msgstr "前言撤回は無し！"

msgid "Dang."
msgstr "残念。"

msgid "Huh... he's a lot quieter when he's with you."
msgstr "へぇ……そいつ、あんたといる時はずっと静かね。"

msgid "Maybe he's anticipating his demise!?"
msgstr "もしかして、死が間近なのを感じてるとか!?"

msgid "Oh man, can't wait!!!"
msgstr "ああもう、待ちきれない!!!"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.item_caterpillar_on_moth_girl.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "I don't need to see him anymore."
msgstr "もうそいつを見る必要はない。"

msgid "Not ALIVE, at least."
msgstr "少なくとも、生きてる姿はね。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.item_doorknob_on_moth_boy.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Do you know where this leads?"
msgstr "これがどこに通じるドアノブか知ってる？"

msgid "No. We found that lying around when we were setting up camp."
msgstr "ううん。テントを張ったときに、落ちてるのを見つけただけだから。"

msgid "I see..."
msgstr "そう……"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_Lakeside_Tent_Interior.item_doorknob_on_moth_girl.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Do you know where this leads?"
msgstr "これがどこに通じるドアノブか知ってる？"

msgid "No idea."
msgstr "さあね。"

msgid "Please, we already gave you the doorknob."
msgstr "やめて、もうドアノブは渡したでしょ。"

msgid "What more do you want?"
msgstr "これ以上何が望みなの？"

msgid "Oh god..."
msgstr "うぐ……"

msgid "Please stop, I seriously can't stand that."
msgstr "やめて、本気で耐えられない。"

msgid "Get that shit away from me."
msgstr "そのクソを早くどけて。"

msgid "Hate that crap."
msgstr "ゲロほど嫌いなの。"

msgid "Alright alright geez!"
msgstr "ああもう、わかったわよ！"

msgid "Just take the stupid doorknob and leave!"
msgstr "このバカげたドアノブはあげるから、早くどっか行って！"

msgid "That smells putrid..."
msgstr "その花、吐きそうな臭いがすんのよ……"

msgid "I guess I get to keep him...?"
msgstr "この子は私が持ってていいってこと……？"

msgid "No thanks, I don't care for stones."
msgstr "いらない、石には興味ないから。"

msgid "The heck would I need that for?"
msgstr "それを私にどうしろっての？"

msgid "I don't know."
msgstr "さあ。"

msgid "To give to Rune..?"
msgstr "ルーンに渡すとか……？"

msgid "Who the heck is Rune?"
msgstr "ルーンって誰よ？"

msgid "What in the world are you doing!?"
msgstr "いったい何してんのよ!?"

msgid "Maybe she's deranged."
msgstr "気が狂ったのかも。"

msgid "You said to kill it."
msgstr "殺せって言ったでしょ。"

msgid "Yeah, so do it already!"
msgstr "そうよ、だから早くして！"

msgid "(Hmmm...)"
msgstr "(うーん……)"

msgid "(I guess salt doesn't work on moths.)"
msgstr "(蛾には塩は効かないみたい。)"

msgid "What. The. FUCK."
msgstr "何。なの。よ。"

msgid "...Oh man..."
msgstr "……あーあ……"

msgid "A fireplace."
msgstr "焚き火。"

msgid "(There's no smoke...?)"
msgstr "(煙が全然出てない……？)"

msgid "Take ${item:ch1.forest_caterpillar}?"
msgstr "${item:ch1.forest_caterpillar} を拾う？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "拾う"

msgid "No"
msgstr "拾わない"
